                      "ep_id": 46,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Zhongli_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "鍾離",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "鍾離自身的護盾可以降低敵人物理抗性，而且鍾離自身的攻擊段數較高，因此在四星武器中，該武器很適合物理輸出型的鍾離。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 33,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Rosaria_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "蘿莎莉亞",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器適合物理輸出型的羅莎莉亞。羅莎莉亞作為冰元素角色，比較好觸發超導來減少敵人物抗，一命增加攻擊速度也會增加該武器技能被動觸發次數。駐場物理流的羅莎莉亞可以發揮它的優點，比較適合使用該武器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
